data.name: Si-el, the Vacuous
data.notes: "Si-el, the Vacuous" is an Oc-serv laying dormant on the floor in Qing Long Glade in the central area of Noctilum (just south from the Qing Long Glade basecamp). Dormant Oc-servs will typically only awaken to attack Skells but by using area of effect attacks on nearby targets which then indirectly damage the sleepy Oc-servs they can be drawn into combat while on foot.
